    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to text-based description of images. These texts offer the equivalent information that a sighted reader would get when looking at a picture, but intended as an accessibility aid for those who are blind or visually impaired. Image descriptions may be in an image caption, in a text post, or shared in a text link for extended descriptions.</Note_Text>
